title: Onimiya-sensei no Kiss ni wa Sakaraenai
original_name: 鬼宮先生のキスには逆らえない
sinopse:
Staying together with a sadist teacher!?

A poor high school girl, Moka has to work for her living everyday. The rescue came from her admired teacher, Onimiya, but… Sensei's true self is a sadist!? What will her life be now!?

(Source: Chibi Manga)
